{"word":"G5534 - χρή - chrḗ - khray - Ought","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>chrḗ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khray"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Ought"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஒருவரையும் கூட்டிக்குறிக்காத வினைச்சொல் - இரு, தேவையானதாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"it is necessary"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Third person singular of the same as <a href=\"#/G5530 - χράομαι - chráomai - khrah'-om-ahee/5530\">G5530</a> or <a href=\"#/G5531 - χράω - chráō - khrah'-o/5531\">G5531</a> used impersonally; it <i>needs</i> (<i>must</i> or <i>should</i>) be: - ought."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}